### Step 1: Register new employee with the test token
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

token=test-token-12345&name=John Doe&email=john@example.com&password=password123

###

### Step 2: Login with the newly registered user // PO LOGIRANJE KOPIRAJ GO TOKENOT OD RESPONSE
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

email=john@example.com&password=password123

###

### Step 3: Access protected endpoint WITHOUT token (should fail 401)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/devices

###

### Step 4: Access protected endpoint WITH valid token // POSLE BEARER OSTAVI 1 PRAZNO MESTO I KOPIRAJ GO TOKENOT OD STEP 2 
GET http://localhost:8080/api/devices
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJqb2huQGV4YW1wbGUuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc4MjQ4MzkzLCJleHAiOjE3NzgzMzQ3OTN9.plFpwYhHHUMua8HB3Lgk_JgWznvHEPA2aUUazhreOyc

###

### Step 5: Access protected endpoint WITH invalid token (should fail 401)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/devices
Authorization: Bearer invalid-token-xyz